The paper discusses the design of middleware for the Internet of Things, which involves distributed computing and networking (cs.DC) as well as software engineering (cs.SE). The focus is on the communication and integration of edge devices, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions data pre-processing, which is a common task in data science (cs.DS).
